skills.description:
(Test Server) Increases Total DMG against enemies of countered types by 30.0%. CD of the active skill is refreshed when using Ult. This effect has 10s of CD.
Herrscher of Thunder equip bonus: During Ult and Finisher, all skill timers and the stage timer are paused; Each entry restores 200 Herrscher energy. CD: 10;
If the active skill is used in the burst state, the dragon stays on the field as a summoned entity after releasing Finisher till the host exits, releases Bombard. When the dragon is on the field, the host stays in Herrscher Form. The dragon obtains energy equal to the host's current Herrscher Charge up to 600. Energy consumetion of Bombard becomes 200% and DMG dealt becomes 70% DMG of the host's DMG. When the energy is depleted, the dragon stays more than 10s, or the host use Ult again, the dragon exits.
